sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>(Envoy/AgentGW/Istio)<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP<br/>(Inference Scheduler)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant Prefill as Prefill Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Decode as Decode Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant DecodeBackend as Decode Backend<br/>8200/TCP HTTP
    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Decode: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Optimized Baseline)
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
        GW->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc request<br/>9002/TCP
        Note over EPP: Evaluate pod metrics:<br/>- prefix cache affinity<br/>- load-aware balancing<br/>- queue depth signals
        EPP->>GW: ext-proc response<br/>(selected endpoint)
        GW->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
        Decode-->>GW: Streaming response<br/>HTTP/8000
        GW-->>Client: Streaming response<br/>HTTP/80
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Client,DecodeBackend: Flow 2: Prefill/Decode Disaggregation
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
        GW->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc request<br/>9002/TCP
        Note over EPP: Select prefill pod<br/>(cache-aware)
        EPP->>GW: ext-proc response<br/>(prefill endpoint)
        GW->>Prefill: Forward to prefill<br/>HTTP/8000
        Note over Prefill: Execute prefill phase<br/>(compute KV cache)
        Prefill->>DecodeBackend: NIXL KV Transfer<br/>5600/TCP (RDMA/TCP)
        Note over DecodeBackend: Receive KV cache<br/>(zero-copy if RDMA)
        Sidecar->>EPP: Decode notification<br/>HTTP/8000
        DecodeBackend-->>Sidecar: Streaming tokens
        Sidecar-->>GW: Streaming response
        GW-->>Client: Streaming response<br/>HTTP/80
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Decode,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading (Startup)
        Decode->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 (HF_TOKEN Bearer)
        S3-->>Decode: Model artifacts
        Note over Decode: Load model into<br/>GPU/accelerator memory
        Decode->>Prom: Expose /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Prefill,DecodeBackend: Flow 4: Wide Expert-Parallelism (Multi-Node)
        Note over Prefill,DecodeBackend: Worker 0 (Leader) coordinates Workers 1..N
        Prefill->>DecodeBackend: data-parallel RPC<br/>5555/TCP gRPC
        Note over Prefill,DecodeBackend: NVSHMEM/RDMA all-to-all<br/>GPU Direct (ibgda transport)<br/>Requires IPC_LOCK capability
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over Decode,OTEL: Observability (Optional)
        Decode->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>gRPC/4317
        Decode->>Prom: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8000 /metrics
        EPP->>Prom: Scrape EPP metrics<br/>HTTP/9090 /metrics
    end
